***** Required Texts *****
[Amazon_logo] Williams, J. H., Jr. Fundamentals of Applied Dynamics. New York,
NY: John Wiley and Sons, Inc., 2006. ISBN: 9780470133859. (Williams)
***** Recommended Texts *****
[Amazon_logo] Bedford, A., and Wallace L. Fowler. Engineering Mechanics:
Dynamics. 2nd ed. Menlo Park, CA: Addison-Wesley Publishing, Inc., 1998. ISBN:
9780201180718. (Bedford and Fowler)
The readings consist of selected chapters from Williams and the lecture_notes.
